### Register a new user
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "userName": "testuser",
  "phone": "+237650123456",
  "firstName": "Test",
  "surName": "User"
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "yvesdylane24@gmail.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

